A script to format code in specified folders/files using Phpstorms formatting tool

Installation:

clone this repo (visit the maru bitbucket and find marumatchbox/formatter) into the folder where you keep all of your dev projects

define your Phpstorm's main bin folder (where phpstorm.sh is located) in the config file
define your project folder in the config file

specify the folders or files you want to format in the "directories" file 

Use:

cd into this folder (where this readme file is located)

run the script by entering "bash formatter.sh" or "./formatter.sh" in your terminal

done! now all your files should be formatted according to the style found in "format/team_format.xml"


